# AEM Bulk Publisher — AI Agent Rules & Architecture Guideline

Welcome to the **AEM Bulk Publisher** repository. This file defines the architecture, flows, and AppSec requirements for any AI Agent working on this codebase.

---

## 📌 Project Context

- **Name:** AEM Bulk Publisher
- **Type:** Google Chrome Extension (Manifest V3)
- **Author:** VML Argentina - Automation Squad
- **Current Version:** 1.3.0
- **Purpose:** Allows bulk upload and quick injection of paths into the 'Manage Publication' wizard in Adobe Experience Manager (AEM) as a Cloud Service, automating the manual process.
- **Target AEM:** AEM as a Cloud Service `https://*.adobeaemcloud.com/*`
- **API:** Does not use an external API. Interacts directly with the Coral UI DOM on the Manage Publication screen.

