## 🧩 Module Integration Conventions

When adding a new module:

1. Create a folder in `modules/[name]/`
2. `popup-[name].js` — UI logic and triggers
3. `content-[name].js` — Page/API logic
4. Register the content script in `manifest.json`
5. Append the script tag at the end of `core/popup.html`
6. Update `core/modules-info.js`
7. Document in this file and in `Readme.md`

